    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors achieved their required levels under MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts hemolysis index within 8.3% mean relative error of experimental measurements, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all 5 operating conditions. The credibility body of evidence is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for this Class II CPB device.",
